data.description: Discover a stunning 4-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom residence positioned on a generous corner lot in the highly desired Timberwood Park area, promising a unique blend of comfort, elegance, and endless possibilities for entertainment and relaxation. The home's beautiful curb appeal invites you into a world where modern conveniences meet cozy living, featuring a spacious living area adorned with custom-built shelving and a warming fireplace. The heart of the home, a modern kitchen, is equipped with ample cabinetry, countertops, an electric inlay stovetop, and stainless steel appliances, catering to both the casual cook and the aspiring chef. Not to be overlooked, a media room offers additional space for entertainment or relaxation. Retreat to the primary bedroom, showcasing a stylish barn door that opens to an on-suite bathroom with a separate large shower and standalone tub, providing a private sanctuary within your home. Each bedroom is thoughtfully designed with space and comfort in mind. Step outside to discover your outdoor oasis, featuring an outdoor kitchen, deck area, and ample grassy space, perfect for gatherings or quiet evenings under the stars. Located in Timberwood Park, this home not only offers a serene living environment but also proximity to excellent schools, great shopping, and dining, making it an ideal setting for creating lasting memories.   30 Acre Private Park
